        "committer": {
          "name": "Oleg Drokin",
          "email": "oleg.drokin@intel.com",
          "date": "2016-05-18 01:35:38.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-8139 ofd: Make ofd.max_brw to take number prefixes",
        "message": "LU-8139 ofd: Make ofd.max_brw to take number prefixes\n\nofd.max_brw control is written to take input in megabytes,\nbut it does not have _mb in the name making it confusing.\n\nChange the code to accept prefixes like K and M, but also assume\nthat if no prefix was specified, it means M.\n\nUpdate display output to show M after the number too, though\nthat loses precision since new scheme of things allows you\nto set fractional megabytes too.\n\nChange-Id: I2ac5331698fe70a5626c1dd77217b868578fa66c\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
